@baseUrl = https://localhost:7293

### Complete Exam Flow Test - From Start to Finish

### PHASE 1: EXAM SETUP

### 1. Create New Exam
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maDeThi": "TEST_FLOW_001",
  "tenDeThi": "Test Complete Exam Flow",
  "thoiGianLamBai": 30,
  "thoiGianBatDau": "2024-12-20T10:00:00",
  "trangThai": "Active",
  "danhSachIdCauHoi": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
}

### 2. Get Active Exams (Verify exam was created)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/active
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Exam Details by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/code/TEST_FLOW_001
Accept: application/json

### PHASE 2: STUDENT STARTS EXAM

### 4. Start Exam Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maDeThi": "TEST_FLOW_001",
  "thietBiUserAgent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36",
  "ip": "192.168.1.100"
}

### 5. Get Exam Questions (Use baithiId from previous response)
# Replace {baithiId} with actual ID from start exam response
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/questions
Accept: application/json

### 6. Check Initial Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/progress
Accept: application/json

### PHASE 3: STUDENT ANSWERS QUESTIONS

### 7. Save Answer for Question 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 1,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 1,
  "daLuu": true
}

### 8. Save Answer for Question 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 2,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 1,
  "daLuu": true
}

### 9. Save Answer for Question 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 3,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 3,
  "daLuu": true
}

### 10. Check Progress After Answering
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/progress
Accept: application/json

### 11. Save Draft Answer (not final)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 4,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 1,
  "daLuu": false
}

### 12. Update Draft Answer to Final
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 4,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 2,
  "daLuu": true
}

### PHASE 4: ANTI-CHEAT MONITORING

### 13. Log Tab Switch Warning
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/warning
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "loaiCanhBao": "TAB_SWITCH",
  "moTa": "Student switched to Google Chrome tab"
}

### 14. Log Copy/Paste Warning
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/warning
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "loaiCanhBao": "COPY_PASTE",
  "moTa": "Detected copy/paste activity"
}

### 15. Check Warning Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/warnings
Accept: application/json

### PHASE 5: EXAM SUBMISSION

### 16. Submit Complete Exam
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "danhSachCauTraLoi": [
    {
      "idBaiThi": 3,
      "idCauHoi": 1,
      "idLuaChonDaChon": 1,
      "daLuu": true
    },
    {
      "idBaiThi": 3,
      "idCauHoi": 2,
      "idLuaChonDaChon": 1,
      "daLuu": true
    },
    {
      "idBaiThi": 3,
      "idCauHoi": 3,
      "idLuaChonDaChon": 3,
      "daLuu": true
    },
    {
      "idBaiThi": 3,
      "idCauHoi": 4,
      "idLuaChonDaChon": 2,
      "daLuu": true
    },
    {
      "idBaiThi": 3,
      "idCauHoi": 5,
      "idLuaChonDaChon": 2,
      "daLuu": true
    }
  ]
}

### 17. Verify Final Progress (Should show completed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/progress
Accept: application/json

### 18. Try to Access Questions After Submission (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/3/questions
Accept: application/json

### 19. Try to Save Answer After Submission (Should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBaiThi": 3,
  "idCauHoi": 1,
  "idLuaChonDaChon": 2,
  "daLuu": true
}

### PHASE 6: VERIFICATION

### 20. Get Random Questions (Test other functionality)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi/random?count=5
Accept: application/json

### SUCCESS CRITERIA:
# - Exam created successfully
# - Student can start exam
# - Questions loaded correctly
# - Answers saved properly
# - Warnings logged accurately
# - Exam submitted successfully
# - Post-submission access denied